(n, k, c)
h(X) \geq c/2
h(X) = \operatorname{inf}_{A, B \subseteq V, A \cup B=V, A \cap B = \emptyset} \frac{|E(A,B)|}{min(|A|, |B|)}.
 \frac{|\partial A|}{(n-|A|)|A|} \geq c/n.  
h(X) \geq c/2
A \subseteq V
h(X) = \frac{|E(A, B)|}{min(|A|, |B|)}
B=V - A
 | \partial A | \leq |E(A, B)|
A \cup B = V, A \cap B = \emptyset
max(|A|, |B|) \geq n/2
 c/2 \leq \frac{n|\partial A|}{2|B| |A|} \leq \frac{n|E(A, B)|}{2|B| |A|} \\ = \frac{n|E(A, B)|}{2 max(|B|, |A|)min(|B|, |A|)} \leq \frac{|E(A, B)|}{min(|B|, |A|)} = h(X). 
